data.description: Lovely 5-bedroom, 3.5 bathroom traditional home on a finished basement nestled on 1.8 acres in the sought-after TOP school district! This classic residence boasts front and side porches, well-kept landscaping, and charming curb appeal. The kitchen comes equipped with a breakfast area, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances, perfect for entertaining. As you enter, you're greeted by a welcoming foyer leading to the dining room and living room/study. The comfortable great room, featuring a fireplace, seamlessly connects to the kitchen, maintaining a cozy atmosphere. Upstairs, you'll find the owner's suite with a tray ceiling, dual vanities, and a nice soaking tub and separate shower. Three additional bedrooms, a full bath, and a bonus room await upstairs, providing ample space for family and guests. The finished basement, with its own private entrance, includes a kitchen, guest room, full bath, and flexible space ideal for a recreational area or home office. Outside, the fenced backyard offers plenty of room for outdoor living and entertaining, perfect for creating your own oasis with a swimming pool. Elinburg is a welcoming HOA community with amenities including a swimming pool and playground, all with low annual dues. This home truly has it all!
